'''佛罗里达新学院'''（'''New College of Florida'''）是位于美國[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[萨拉索塔_(佛罗里达州)|萨拉索塔]]的一所公立[[美国文理学院|文理学院]]，为[[佛羅里達州立大學系統|佛羅里達州立大學系統]]成員<ref>{{cite web|title = Fast Facts|publisher = New College of Florida|url = http://www.ncf.edu/fast-facts|accessdate = 2011-01-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110108120141/http://www.ncf.edu/fast-facts|archive-date = 2011-01-08|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=New College of Florida|publisher=State University System of Florida|url=http://www.flbog.org/aboutsus/universities/ncf.php|accessdate=2001-01-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080204183234/http://www.flbog.org/aboutsus/universities/ncf.php|archivedate=2008-02-04}}</ref>。該學院创立于1960年，资金来自于[[联合基督教会|联合基督教会]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ncf.edu/about/history.html |title=A Brief History - New College of Florida, The public liberal arts honors college for the state of Florida |accessdate=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2008-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080620021736/http://www.ncf.edu/about/history.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在2020年《[[美國新聞與世界報道|美國新聞與世界報道]]》的“全国文理学院”排名中列在第84位。<ref name="USnews">{{cite web|title=New College of Florida|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/new-college-of-florida-153704|publisher=[[美國新聞與世界報道|美國新聞與世界報道]]|accessdate=2016-10-28|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220025108/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/new-college-of-florida-153704|dead-url=no}}</ref>

